title: Jasc Animation Shop 3
description:
Animation Shop provides the tools you need to easily add animated buttons, banners and other cool effects to your web site. animation shop will provide the tools you need to easily add banners, animated buttons and other cool effects to your web site and to create effective business presentations.
Used as a standalone program or as a complement to Jasc Paint Shop Pro is a great communication tool that helps you stand out from the crowd on the web or in presentations - and get your message across in a fun, interesting way.
